{"tid":2073483,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[急] 6月25日前要核對選民資料","createTime":"2020-06-21T11:08:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-24T14:33:09.000Z","uid":179649,"like":18,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":30,"replies":[{"pid":"c1efe2e3889ad0acac6e5883a7b724595625c604","tid":2073483,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:08:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://www.voterregistration.gov.hk/images/20_voter03.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.voterregistration.gov.hk%2Fimages%2F20_voter03.jpg&h=9edb9b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/welcome.jsp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.voterinfo.gov.hk%2Fbd_reovi%2FOVIES%2Fjsp%2Fmob%2Fwelcome.jsp&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Yz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=31b136b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www2.voterinfo.gov.hk/bd_reovi/OVIES/jsp/mob/welcome.jsp</a><br />\n<br />\n上面link入去望番自己地區，有無超區(二）<br />\n如果資料有錯快d更正番<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d41bee74000f20d16fa2421750e830dbdb07f4ad","tid":2073483,"uid":264245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:11:58.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f4f31481c57352abe7682bbda99a483a50c98f5e","tid":2073483,"uid":197086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:22:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f60b8d5779f17d071562d09541641e750a725ab0","tid":2073483,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:28:50.000Z","msg":"推到25號<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"18e3804269d71731fb7793eec9b4669b3e629925","tid":2073483,"uid":20727,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:32:49.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"1abb9d7d51f9427ed82db106595dec247f056287","tid":2073483,"uid":7435,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T11:34:56.000Z","msg":"新登記係咪唔洗核對<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b08e8c8b03c557df0e5c66cdb0af197893e2b18","tid":2073483,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"點樣叫做有超區？<br />\n見到只有功能界別"},{"pid":"2f0c1756ed334de2026af42937ed104e997bc5b2","tid":2073483,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0b08e8c8b03c557df0e5c66cdb0af197893e2b18","tid":2073483,"uid":21432,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T12:35:41.000Z","msg":"點樣叫做有超區？<br />\n見到只有功能界別"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:10:17.000Z","msg":"係功能界別(二)先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n區議會（第二）功能界別<br />\n登記成為區議會（第二）功能界別選民<br />\n<br />\n合資格人士<br />\n<br />\n如你已登記為地方選區的選民，但沒有登記為任何功能界別的選民，你便符合資格登記成為區議會（第二）功能界別（即俗稱的「超級區議會」功能界別）選民。<br />\n<br />\n若你已在現有的功能界別（鄉議局功能界別、漁農界功能界別、保險界功能界別、航運交通界功能界別及區議會（第一）功能界別除外）中登記，你亦可以更改功能界別，登記為區議會（第二）功能界別的選民。欲知區議會（第二）功能界別的登記資格詳情，請按下列連結：<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/dc2fc.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reo.gov.hk%2Fch%2Fvoter%2Fdc2fc.htm&d=CgUtGs1XjGBKDnLe79D2Yz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=e7b1e001\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.reo.gov.hk/ch/voter/dc2fc.htm</a>"},{"pid":"5952152fda510f8be72c543122cab829bd43f455","tid":2073483,"uid":179649,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cheerup.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d99eccbc430c6ffd259eff5b7fe2190cd06921b4","tid":2073483,"uid":189523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-21T13:31:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f5e4660a5b0482cdaa055b0c92322a39a9e38e7